{"id":44201,"date":"2024-01-01T10:12:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-01T04:42:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=44201"},"modified":"2024-02-08T21:37:35","modified_gmt":"2024-02-08T16:07:35","slug":"folding-bed-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/folding-bed-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"11 Impressive Folding Bed Ideas to Maximise Your Space"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Make space in your home with unique folding bed ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Folding beds are the perfect space savers and can be easily tucked away when not in use. Learn how to transform a folding bed into something more creative and functional.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to folding beds, there are many options on the market. From bunk beds to full-sized furniture, these foldable beds provide everything you need to maximise your space while still getting the same quality sleep as in a regular bed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a folding bed, you can maximise your space and make sleeping more comfortable. You can use it as an extra bed or a guest bed in your house. People who have small rooms can also use folding beds to create more space in their rooms.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Folding beds are also known as fold-away beds. They have many features such as built-in storage, drawers, extra bed and other space-saving mechanisms that help you utilise less space. Many fold-away beds offer many benefits, such as saving space and making things easier when moving around the house. Folding beds come in different sizes and specifications depending on their purpose for usage. Read along to learn about the best folding beds available in the market.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Folding Bed For An Earthy Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wood has a charm of its own. It lends an earthy look to your modern space. The design looks classy and elegant yet takes up no extra space in your home. If you are looking for intelligent options to add some cosiness to your bedroom, this folding bed is perfect.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131551\/wooden-folding-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden folding bed with a classy and elegant appearance that helps save space\" class=\"wp-image-44214\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131551\/wooden-folding-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131551\/wooden-folding-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131551\/wooden-folding-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131551\/wooden-folding-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A space-saving wooden folding bed to add extra space at home.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Folding Bed With Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This wall-mounted bed comes with some hidden storage. You can hide away all your essentials and keep your home clutter-free. The bookshelf is excellent for showcasing your extensive collection of books and aesthetic artefacts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131515\/modern-folding-bed-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Modern folding bed with hidden storage to keep your home clutter-free\" class=\"wp-image-44208\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131515\/modern-folding-bed-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131515\/modern-folding-bed-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131515\/modern-folding-bed-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131515\/modern-folding-bed-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern folding bed with storage for a clutter-free home.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Folding Bed Perfect For Kids&#8217; Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for smart space-saving furniture ideas for your kids&#8217; room? You can opt for this single folding bed that quickly turns into a double bed. This will help save a lot of floor space, and yet be always ready to host your kids&#8217; friends for their happening pyjama parties.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131521\/single-folding-bed-for-kids-room.jpg\" alt=\"Single folding bed, perfect for a kids' room, that quickly turns into a double bed\" class=\"wp-image-44209\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131521\/single-folding-bed-for-kids-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131521\/single-folding-bed-for-kids-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131521\/single-folding-bed-for-kids-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131521\/single-folding-bed-for-kids-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Folding bed designs for your kids&#8217; room interiors.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall Mounted Folding Bed For Maximum Floor Space<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of space constraints, sometimes we have a very cramped bedroom after placing the bed. But now, we have developed a unique bed design that fits into the wall. Ample floor space and a comfortable night&#8217;s sleep go hand in hand now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131533\/wall-mounted-folding-bed.jpeg\" alt=\"Wall mounted folding bed saves ample floor space and suits homes of every size\" class=\"wp-image-44211\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131533\/wall-mounted-folding-bed.jpeg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131533\/wall-mounted-folding-bed-300x180.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131533\/wall-mounted-folding-bed-768x461.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/04131533\/wall-mounted-folding-bed-150x90.jpeg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Murphy beds are perfect furniture solutions for homes of every size.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trendy Murphy Bed In White&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This white murphy bed saves space and adds a soothing touch to your bedroom. The clean lines and clutter-free design makes this bedroom one of a kind. You can turn your bedroom into a full-fledged <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/home-office-design\/\">home office<\/a> in no time. If you want a multifunctional home, this design is perfect for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/